portfolio link - https://sachin-port.netlify.app/

Key Features:
About Me Section: A brief introduction to who I am, my background, and my professional journey.
Projects Portfolio: A showcase of selected projects with descriptions, images, and links to the live versions or GitHub repositories.
Skills & Technologies: A visual representation of the programming languages, tools, and technologies I specialize in.
Contact Form: A simple, easy-to-use contact form to get in touch with me for potential opportunities or collaborations.
Responsive Design: The website is optimized for different screen sizes and devices, ensuring a smooth user experience on both mobile and desktop platforms.
Modern Design: Clean, minimalistic, and contemporary design elements that reflect my personal style and professional image.
Technologies Used:
HTML5 for structure
CSS3 for styling (including Flexbox and Grid for layout)
